// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2026-0675 — Mass File Rename (incransom)
// Status: test | Level: high | ID: 7ffb1297-ed00-5174-b513-754aae9ca9af

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
